description:
The E! Online app has been given a complete makeover! We’ve drastically upgraded the design, packed in all of our great content, and added a ton of new features.  

• Faster videos and revamped news articles that now include photos, videos, and other exciting content.
• View the latest news, photos, and videos on a slick new home screen that’s quick and easy to use. 
• Flip through thousands of gorgeous celebrity photos in all new full-screen galleries. 
• Stay connected with our live streams, so you’ll never miss out on what’s happening on the red carpet. 
• Keep up with the latest styles and trends for everything from fashion to food in our Fabulist section. 
• Stay informed up-to-the minute with push notifications and breaking E! News Now videos. 
• Catch our best clips of your favorite E! Shows like Keeping Up With the Kardashians, Fashion Police, and The Soup. 
• Stay on top of the day's hot topics and trending stars, and keep up with the latest gossip and TV Scoop. 
• Easily share articles, photos, and videos with your friends, and become the go-to entertainment expert. 

E! Online will always be the authority on entertainment and pop culture, and now the app you’ve always loved is better than ever!

For full episode programming, download the E! Now app, available in the App Store.
